--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

2.1 REFERENCE CODE AND DOCUMENTATION — PUBLIC RESEARCH LICENSE

    Subject to the terms of this License, you are granted a worldwide,
    royalty-free, non-exclusive license to:
    (a) use, reproduce, and distribute the Reference Code and Documentation;
    (b) create derivative works of the Reference Code;
    (c) publicly display and perform the Reference Code and Documentation;
    provided that:
    (i)   you retain all copyright, patent, trademark notices, and this
          License in all copies;
    (ii)  you clearly attribute SmallLoong Research as the original author;
    (iii) any derivative works of the Reference Code are distributed under
          this same License.

    参考代码与文档 — 公共研究许可

    依据本许可证条款，您被授予全球范围内、免版税、非独占的许可：
    (a) 使用、复制和分发参考代码与文档；
    (b) 基于参考代码创作衍生作品；
    (c) 公开展示和执行参考代码与文档；
    但须满足以下条件：
    (i)   在所有副本中保留所有版权、专利、商标声明及本许可证；
    (ii)  明确标注原作者为 SmallLoong Research；
    (iii) 参考代码的衍生作品须依据本许可证分发。

2.2 MODEL WEIGHTS — CASE-BY-CASE AUTHORIZATION

    Model Weights are NOT covered by the public license grant in Section 2.1.
    Model Weights are NOT included in the public repository.

    Use of Model Weights requires a separate written authorization from
    SmallLoong Research.

    模型权重 — 逐案授权

    模型权重不在第 2.1 条的公共许可范围内。
    模型权重不包含在公开仓库中。

    使用模型权重需要 SmallLoong Research 另行书面授权。

    To request access | 获取授权：

    (a) Academic institutions in the Chinese mainland (中国大陆学术机构):
        Submit an Academic Use Agreement including institution name, research
        scope, and responsible PI. Free of charge.
        提交学术使用协议，包含机构名称、研究范围和负责人。免费。

    (b) Commercial entities in the Chinese mainland (中国大陆商业实体):
        Submit a Commercial License Application. Terms negotiated per use case.
        提交商业许可申请。按使用场景谈判条款。

    (c) Entities outside the Chinese mainland (中国大陆境外实体):
        Submit a detailed proposal including use case, entity background,
        and compliance declaration. Reviewed case-by-case.
        提交详细方案，包含用途、实体背景和合规声明。逐案审核。


