    本许可证须遵守中华人民共和国所有适用的出口管制法律法规。

3.2 Model Weights shall not be exported, re-exported, or transferred to:
    (a) any entity or individual subject to technology transfer restrictions
        under applicable Chinese law;
    (b) any military, intelligence, or surveillance organization;
    (c) any jurisdiction where such transfer is prohibited.

    模型权重不得出口、再出口或转让至：
    (a) 受适用中国法律技术转让限制的任何实体或个人；
    (b) 任何军事、情报或监控组织；
    (c) 禁止此类转让的任何司法管辖区。

3.3 Any person or entity receiving Model Weights under a separate authorization
    may NOT further distribute, sublicense, or transfer the Model Weights to
    any third party without explicit written consent from SmallLoong Research.

    任何依据另行授权获得模型权重的个人或实体，未经 SmallLoong Research 明确书面同意，
    不得进一步分发、转授权或转让模型权重给任何第三方。


