    SmallLoong Research。

4.2 The DaoTi (道体) name, the TrigramSpace architecture, the Degenerate Ground
    State theory, and the HeLuo Ladder Network design are original intellectual
    property of SmallLoong Research. This License does not grant any trademark
    rights.

    道体(DaoTi)名称、三爻空间(TrigramSpace)架构、退化基态理论以及河洛阶梯网络
    (HeLuo Ladder Network)设计是 SmallLoong Research 的原创知识产权。
    本许可证不授予任何商标权利。


